1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,793
Muj sen...

2
00:00:01,793 --> 00:00:04,921
...ta cista bila laska...

3
00:00:04,921 --> 00:00:08,717
...promneni se na kridla.

4
00:00:08,717 --> 00:00:12,262
Tak,aby andeluv malicek sliboval...

5
00:00:12,262 --> 00:00:17,100
...ze se vyplni.

6
00:00:21,271 --> 00:00:24,357
Treba tvuj profil...

7
00:00:24,357 --> 00:00:27,902
...jen se mi mihl pred ocima...

8
00:00:27,902 --> 00:00:31,865
...a moje srdce se rozbusilo.

9
00:00:35,577 --> 00:00:38,663
Kdyz slisim tvuj hlas...

10
00:00:38,663 --> 00:00:42,125
...hlas,ktery mluvi.

11
00:00:42,125 --> 00:00:48,048
Tak vim o tobe zase neco vic. 

12
00:00:49,341 --> 00:00:55,930
Lituji ze nemam tolik odvahy...

13
00:00:56,389 --> 00:01:03,021
...podivat se ti primo do oci. 

14
00:01:03,980 --> 00:01:05,815
Muj sen...

15
00:01:05,815 --> 00:01:08,902
...ta cista bila laska...

16
00:01:08,902 --> 00:01:12,655
...promneni se na kridla.

17
00:01:12,655 --> 00:01:16,201
Tak,aby andeluv malicek sliboval...

18
00:01:16,201 --> 00:01:21,122
...ze se vyplni.

19
00:01:34,177 --> 00:01:38,014
Hej, Yukino! Pospes si,
hned vychazime...

20
00:01:43,770 --> 00:01:46,189
Aaa ... o co je?

21
00:01:47,190 --> 00:01:47,816
Mam te rad!

22
00:01:47,816 --> 00:01:48,400
Co?!

23
00:01:48,401 --> 00:01:49,401
Vecne
roztrouseni

24
00:01:51,111 --> 00:01:53,530
Dnes,cela rodina jedeme
navstivit dedu.

25
00:01:53,863 --> 00:01:55,782
Po dlouhe dobe ho navstivime.

26
00:01:56,991 --> 00:02:01,371
Yukino, jses tak neobycejne podobna
svoji mame.

27
00:02:01,996 --> 00:02:05,291
Nekdy kdyz te vidim,tak se mi zda,
jako bych videl tvoji mamu zamlada..

28
00:02:06,209 --> 00:02:08,128
Poznali jste se,jeste kdyz jte byly detmi, pravda?

29
00:02:08,962 --> 00:02:09,921
Pravda.

30
00:02:10,505 --> 00:02:12,799
Bavili jsme se cely rok.

31
00:02:13,258 --> 00:02:16,970
On vzdycky vymyslel hloupe,a 
nebezpecne zabavy.

32
00:02:17,804 --> 00:02:21,474
Tahal me za sebou,kdyz jsme odnekud utikali,
je to neprijemna historie.

33
00:02:22,183 --> 00:02:24,978
Och,i nyni mam zimnici jakmile si na to vzpomenu.

34
00:02:25,770 --> 00:02:30,025
Ano,byl jsem trochu divocejsi

35
00:02:30,191 --> 00:02:32,277
Nevypada,ze by z toho letos vyrostl.

36
00:02:32,402 --> 00:02:35,864
Vsechno se zmenilo,kdyz jsem se na stredni skole
zamiloval do vasi mamy.

37
00:02:36,197 --> 00:02:39,075
Mela tehdy tolik let,kolik mas ted ty Yukino.

38
00:02:39,367 --> 00:02:41,494
Tak tedy,jak ti nekdy pripadam Yukino ...

39
00:02:42,579 --> 00:02:49,085
...musim si obcas pripomenout,ze jsi moje dcera a ne 
zena.To je doopravdy divny pocit..

40
00:02:50,253 --> 00:02:51,921
Dalsi zastavka je ...

41
00:02:54,341 --> 00:02:56,259
Ahoj, dedo.!

42
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,845
Ach konecne ste tu.

43
00:02:59,512 --> 00:03:01,723
Jsem rad ze jste prijeli..
Pojdte,pojdte..

44
00:03:01,890 --> 00:03:03,183
Ahoj!

45
00:03:06,019 --> 00:03:07,979
Proc mi zaviras dvere pred nosem?!

46
00:03:07,979 --> 00:03:10,190
Nejsi tu vitany!
Vrat se domu.

47
00:03:10,732 --> 00:03:13,735
Tata a Mama byli hodne mladi,kdyz se rozhodli vzit.

48
00:03:13,735 --> 00:03:19,074
Deda tehdy zbil tatu.
Od te doby,se memaji radi.

49
00:03:19,616 --> 00:03:20,658
Och ne, znou...

50
00:03:20,867 --> 00:03:25,705
Moje drahe, vsechny jste zkrasnely,od te
doby co jste tu byly naposled.

51
00:03:26,247 --> 00:03:28,416
Tri krasne sestry.

52
00:03:29,668 --> 00:03:33,088
Tak krasne jste vyrostly,pod dohledem,
takoveho beznadejneho a nekompentniho otce.

53
00:03:33,463 --> 00:03:38,510
Jste takove krasne vnucky!
Az se mi v oku trci slza..

54
00:03:39,344 --> 00:03:41,888
Cholera,podnamitelsky,stary prdola,
Jako vzdy...

55
00:03:42,138 --> 00:03:45,100
Jen proto ze mi ted nadava,je ted na koni.

56
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:48,228
Ty senilni,letos si konecne zestarl!

57
00:03:48,311 --> 00:03:49,562
Ty taky!Otce!

58
00:03:50,605 --> 00:03:52,232
Tak vypadaji ti,co malo vydelavaji.

59
00:03:53,274 --> 00:03:55,902
Neopovazuj se mluvit o me praci!

60
00:04:01,783 --> 00:04:03,284
Zmlkni, smrkaci!

61
00:04:03,702 --> 00:04:07,580
Nikdy nemuzes rozumnet,co znamena odevzdat
svou jednou dcerku,takovemu smrkacovi jako jsi ty.

62
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:10,083
To je problem vsech lidi,kterym se
narodi dcera!

63
00:04:10,083 --> 00:04:13,586
podle tebe penize jsou nejdulezitejsi!
To neni pravda!
Nejdulezitejsi je dobre srdce!

64
00:04:13,586 --> 00:04:14,921
Laska je nejdulezitejsi!
Laska,ktera jde ze srdce!

65
00:04:14,921 --> 00:04:16,673
Laska?Ale di!

66
00:04:16,673 --> 00:04:17,716
Muj ty boze,laska!

67
00:04:17,716 --> 00:04:20,093
Divej co tu napisu!
L.. A.. S..K..A..!

68
00:04:20,093 --> 00:04:22,220
Nech... toho ...tyy!

69
00:04:22,804 --> 00:04:26,349
Ha ha, chces si to vzit?
Musis me nejprve chytit!
Delej,pane Lasko!

70
00:04:26,558 --> 00:04:29,144
Nenecham to takovemu staremu dedkovi!

71
00:04:29,144 --> 00:04:32,981
At te trefi slak, doopravdy dej mi to!

72
00:04:32,981 --> 00:04:36,276
Divejte, je to jak video jak byly mladsi.

73
00:04:37,027 --> 00:04:40,238
Wow, vypadas uplne jako sestricka.

74
00:04:40,405 --> 00:04:42,574
Nyni uz tomu rozumim,doopravdy si ste podobne!

75
00:04:42,657 --> 00:04:45,285
Ve skutecnosti nevim co mam rict,jsem podobna nebo ne!

76
00:04:45,285 --> 00:04:49,205
Hej, cozpak nebyla krasna?!
Ona je i nadale krasna!!

77
00:04:49,289 --> 00:04:51,833
Yukino, opravdu vypadas jak Miyako.

78
00:04:51,833 --> 00:04:54,794
Bud ted ostrazita a nedej se chytit,nejakemu
prastenemu chlapcovi,jo?

79
00:04:55,670 --> 00:04:57,047
Ale ja uz mam chlapce!

80
00:04:58,006 --> 00:04:59,466
Oh jo!

81
00:04:59,466 --> 00:05:02,344
Hmm, je to velmi hodny clovek.!

82
00:05:02,844 --> 00:05:04,637
Co to ma znamenat!
Odkud je ta nahla akceptovanost?

83
00:05:05,513 --> 00:05:08,058
Vydrzte,jdu koupit veci na obed.

84
00:05:08,475 --> 00:05:10,060
Pockej,pujdu s tebou.

85
00:05:10,352 --> 00:05:11,478
Bez,bez

86
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:13,813
A nos nakupy moji dcerky,

87
00:05:14,356 --> 00:05:15,565
dcerin otrok,kterym jsi..

88
00:05:15,815 --> 00:05:18,193
Prestan me porad pomlouvat!
Ty se me snazis urazit.

89
00:05:18,193 --> 00:05:19,444
Sach Mat!

90
00:05:24,115 --> 00:05:25,867
Mnoho se tu zmenilo, pravda

91
00:05:25,867 --> 00:05:29,079
Jo, bylo tu postaveno mnoho domu.

92
00:05:34,918 --> 00:05:35,960
Vraceji se ti vzpominky, co?

93
00:05:36,211 --> 00:05:39,297
O tak,vezmes si me?

94
00:05:40,048 --> 00:05:40,840
 Rada.

95
00:05:41,508 --> 00:05:42,467
<i> Soumrak.</i>

96
00:05:42,926 --> 00:05:44,344
<i> Mesto se rozblika svetlama.</i>

97
00:05:44,803 --> 00:05:49,099
<i> Odnekud sem dobehl zvuk televize,
je mozno citit vuni vecere,kterou  
nekde nekdo pripravuje.</i>

98
00:05:49,099 --> 00:05:51,476
<i>Vzduch pomalu vita uplnek.</i>

99
00:05:51,601 --> 00:05:53,812
<i> Pamatuju si ten pocit,
 divny,ale moc prijemny.</i>

100
00:05:53,895 --> 00:05:56,690
<i> Takove chvile mi pripominaji moje detstvi</i>

101
00:05:57,357 --> 00:06:01,403
<i> Meho dedu,
Strom na ktery jsem casto lezl.
Pratele.</i>

102
00:06:01,903 --> 00:06:07,200
<i>Pamatuju si na takove stare dny,
jako neco ceho se kdyz vstanu muzu 
dotknout.</i>

103
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,167
Hej, jsi tam!

104
00:06:16,543 --> 00:06:19,379
Hej! Hiro!

105
00:06:20,171 --> 00:06:21,047
Yo!

106
00:06:21,131 --> 00:06:22,757
Otec, 6 let.

107
00:06:22,757 --> 00:06:24,509
Cele jmeno : Hiroyuki Miyazawa.

108
00:06:25,218 --> 00:06:28,054
dale znamy jako : "Maly dabel"

109
00:06:31,099 --> 00:06:34,227
Spoustu casu vymyslel opravdu 
hlupe zabavy.

110
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:36,312
Roznasel vselijake reci,

111
00:06:36,771 --> 00:06:38,648
Bil se se starsima klukama, a vyhraval.

112
00:06:39,024 --> 00:06:41,735
Ukradl kdysi bernardyna,aby
se na nem mohl projet.

113
00:06:41,985 --> 00:06:43,903
Zapasy sumo s kockou, atd atd.

114
00:06:44,279 --> 00:06:46,948
Maly dabel,byl dost znamy ve svem okoli.

115
00:06:46,948 --> 00:06:49,242
a jeho byti naplnovalo strachen,dokonce i dospele.

116
00:06:49,242 --> 00:06:51,911
kteri pred nim sve reci radeji schovavali.

117
00:06:52,704 --> 00:06:54,372
Tehdy take poprve potkal jeho zenu.....

118
00:07:04,966 --> 00:07:06,801
Chcete si s nami hrat, devcata?

119
00:07:08,011 --> 00:07:10,805
Dobre, dobre,
mam pro vas idealni role

120
00:07:11,097 --> 00:07:12,265
Budete..

121
00:07:13,266 --> 00:07:15,310
...zajatcemi!

122
00:07:16,353 --> 00:07:21,775
Jejich prvni schuzka byla odbyta,
jak se dalo domyslet,behem jakesi
hloupe hry.

123
00:07:21,983 --> 00:07:23,777
No dobre,hned vas rozvazeme.

124
00:07:23,943 --> 00:07:25,403
Chceme siusiu!

125
00:07:25,403 --> 00:07:26,154
Co ze?!

126
00:07:26,863 --> 00:07:31,409
Byl absolutne prekvapeny,ze je mily
na male deti.

127
00:07:31,618 --> 00:07:35,497
jak moc se s nim bavili.

128
00:07:36,164 --> 00:07:37,749
Vsichni hotovi?
( schovavana)

129
00:07:38,083 --> 00:07:39,584
Jeste ne!

130
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:41,419
Vsichni hotovi?

131
00:07:41,753 --> 00:07:43,129
Jeste ne!

132
00:07:43,755 --> 00:07:45,173
Tak mam uz jit hledat,nebo ne!

133
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:47,092
Jo!

134
00:07:48,176 --> 00:07:51,137
Hej, tady jsi Hiro!

135
00:07:51,888 --> 00:07:53,098
Co, nasla si ho?

136
00:07:53,098 --> 00:07:54,099
Ne,tu nikdo neni!

137
00:07:54,099 --> 00:07:55,558
Kde je Hiro?

138
00:07:56,184 --> 00:07:57,185
Kde muze byt?

139
00:07:57,185 --> 00:07:58,186
Nikde neni!

140
00:07:58,186 --> 00:07:59,562
Podivame se tam!

141
00:08:04,734 --> 00:08:06,111
Hej, Hiro.

142
00:08:06,569 --> 00:08:07,362
No?

143
00:08:07,904 --> 00:08:11,449
Hiro, je pravda,ze nemas
mamu ani tatu?

144
00:08:11,908 --> 00:08:13,076
Jo, to je pravda.

145
00:08:15,036 --> 00:08:18,832
Um, a vis?
ze ja taky nemam mamu ani tatu?

146
00:08:21,668 --> 00:08:23,586
Myslela jsem ze jsem sama.

147
00:08:24,921 --> 00:08:25,880
Taky sama?

148
00:08:27,007 --> 00:08:27,924
Mej se!

149
00:08:27,924 --> 00:08:29,384
Ahoj!

150
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,888
Dedo, jsem doma!

151
00:08:34,514 --> 00:08:37,851
Vitej doma Hiroyuki.

152
00:08:40,020 --> 00:08:43,023
V tech casech jsem bydlel s dedou,jen ja 
a on.

153
00:08:43,523 --> 00:08:47,819
Byli jsme chudi,bydleli jsme v dome,
co postavili moji rodice,a z uspor meho dedy,

154
00:08:48,611 --> 00:08:52,115
ale nikdy nam nebylo tak zle.

155
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:58,747
Nevzpominal jsem tak vubec na rodice,protoze
doopravdy hodne mam rad sveho dedu....

156
00:09:00,248 --> 00:09:04,502
Je cas bys sesedl z mych kolen,noha me
zacina trochu bolet.

157
00:09:05,754 --> 00:09:09,215
Obvykle jsi takovy loupeznik
a doma se chovas perfektne.

158
00:09:09,215 --> 00:09:11,176
Nikdo nezna tuhle tvoji stranu..

159
00:09:12,135 --> 00:09:13,136
Ne to nevadi,

160
00:09:16,014 --> 00:09:20,268
Dny ubihaly a ja jsem prestal sedat na kolenech meho dedy.

161
00:09:21,353 --> 00:09:23,355
a uz nikdy jsme nespali ve stejnem luzku.

162
00:09:24,314 --> 00:09:27,984
Rozumnel jsem tomu,ze nastal cas,abych byl
vice samostatny a svedomity.

163
00:09:38,036 --> 00:09:40,038
Oh, to jsi ty Hiro!

164
00:09:40,997 --> 00:09:45,502
Wow, my chodime jste do skoly!
A ty uz jsi na gymnaziu!

165
00:09:46,961 --> 00:09:48,380
Vpadam dobre, co?

166
00:09:48,630 --> 00:09:50,215
Vypadas divne!

167
00:09:51,591 --> 00:09:57,389
Ha, ode dneska se vsechno zmeni.
Konec zabavy s detmi a tak.

168
00:09:59,140 --> 00:10:01,434
Ale Hiro, fungujou tvoje hodinky dobre?

169
00:10:01,434 --> 00:10:04,813
Vis ze my devcata,vychazime do skoly
trochu drive...

170
00:10:05,230 --> 00:10:06,773
O sakra..!

171
00:10:06,773 --> 00:10:11,611
Vysel jsem z domu,tak jako bych
porad chodil do zakladky!!

172
00:10:11,986 --> 00:10:13,113
Hiro ...

173
00:10:13,363 --> 00:10:15,156
Jsem... hrozne... opozdily!

174
00:10:15,907 --> 00:10:19,536
Mejte se devcata!
Doufam ze to jeste stihnu, slysite?!

175
00:10:20,495 --> 00:10:26,376
Protoze zacali chodit do ruznych skol,tak
se na nejaky cas rozdelili.

176
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:28,336
Jdeme?

177
00:10:35,176 --> 00:10:37,595
Hiro, Jak muzes byt tak lenivy!?

178
00:10:38,013 --> 00:10:40,181
Dnes prvakum zacinaji prednasky.

179
00:10:40,181 --> 00:10:42,892
Jdeme se podivat jestli tam neni nejaka krasotinka

180
00:10:43,184 --> 00:10:45,979
Chlapi z vyssich rocniku,nam pred
nosem vyfoukly vsechny prima devcata.

181
00:10:46,021 --> 00:10:47,731
Prvni tridy,to je nase jedina sance.

182
00:10:48,148 --> 00:10:49,607
Co je s tym chlapkem?!

183
00:10:50,025 --> 00:10:53,111
Vy mate jakesi brouky v hlave.
Me to vubec nezajima.

184
00:10:53,528 --> 00:10:55,655
Co s tebou chlape. Nebud frajer.
NEumis se pobavit?

185
00:10:55,864 --> 00:10:57,991
Nebo te devcata nezajimaji?
Co?

186
00:10:58,074 --> 00:11:00,118
Hodne devcatum se libis.
Jsi opravdu popularni,vis?

187
00:11:00,368 --> 00:11:02,579
Proc s zadnou nechodis, co?

188
00:11:04,873 --> 00:11:08,835
Ja vubec nechapu,o co se vam jedna!

189
00:11:09,711 --> 00:11:13,173
Tehdy prave,

190
00:11:13,173 --> 00:11:17,177
na 22 Ceremonii zacatku roku,

191
00:11:17,177 --> 00:11:22,098
se znovu potkali....

192
00:11:25,977 --> 00:11:27,479
Oww ...

193
00:11:30,190 --> 00:11:31,649
Sakra, to je holka,

194
00:11:32,859 --> 00:11:34,778
Jsi... jsi v poradku?

195
00:11:46,706 --> 00:11:48,291
Oh, Hiro, jsi to ty?!

196
00:11:48,291 --> 00:11:49,376
He?

197
00:11:49,918 --> 00:11:53,421
Miyako byla prvni divka,o ktere
si myslel ze je nadherna.

198
00:11:57,967 --> 00:12:00,929
Stale casteji jsem mel dojem,ze je
deda cim dal vic slabsi.

199
00:12:01,554 --> 00:12:03,056
Jsem doma., dedo.

200
00:12:04,140 --> 00:12:05,058
V poradku.

201
00:12:06,309 --> 00:12:08,478
Dneska si tu pozdeji, Hiroyuki.

202
00:12:15,568 --> 00:12:16,903
Oh, Hiro.

203
00:12:17,737 --> 00:12:20,448
Oops. Miyazawa-senpai, dobry den

204
00:12:20,615 --> 00:12:25,036
Ha, to je dobre ze ses to konecne naucila:

205
00:12:27,122 --> 00:12:30,875
Nikdy nezapominej,ze jsem
starsi student.

206
00:12:34,004 --> 00:12:34,754
Mej se

207
00:12:54,899 --> 00:12:57,110
Miyako, to je ten kluk,ktery
se ti asi..?

208
00:12:57,944 --> 00:13:01,031
Nebo to neni Miyazawa z vyssi tridy?

209
00:13:01,031 --> 00:13:01,906
Co?

210
00:13:05,243 --> 00:13:07,579
Uh... um...

211
00:13:08,288 --> 00:13:10,874
Um...

212
00:13:33,021 --> 00:13:34,814
Oh, Hiro.

213
00:13:36,524 --> 00:13:40,487
To je prekvapeni!
Nemyslela jsem ze se dostanes
do lyceum Kakarita!

214
00:13:40,695 --> 00:13:44,991
Vzdy ukazujes dojem ze te to nebavi,ale
vzdycky se ucis.

215
00:13:45,033 --> 00:13:48,495
Ha, jsem proste hodne schopny.

216
00:13:48,745 --> 00:13:52,374
Hmm, a co ty,
proc si se prihlasila do meho lycea?

217
00:13:52,916 --> 00:13:57,003
Ocividne, s mymi vysledky to je lehke.

218
00:14:03,301 --> 00:14:07,347
 Jestli nemas jine plany,tak proste pojd do me skoly.

219
00:14:07,681 --> 00:14:10,183
Dobre,tak fajn.

220
00:14:23,071 --> 00:14:27,367
Za chvili prijdou zaci z novych trid.

221
00:14:28,284 --> 00:14:30,662
O co ti jde?
Prece te nezajimala ani Ceremonie na zacatku Roku?

222
00:14:31,037 --> 00:14:32,997
Chces se podivat na nejake studentky, co?

223
00:14:32,997 --> 00:14:35,875
Anebo uz nejakou mas?
A cekas na ni,pravda?

224
00:14:36,209 --> 00:14:37,043
Spravne.

225
00:14:37,335 --> 00:14:38,044
Yo.

226
00:14:41,047 --> 00:14:43,258
Prisla jsi brzo.

227
00:14:46,428 --> 00:14:48,763
Hej Hiro,
Vidim ze chodis do prace.

228
00:14:48,805 --> 00:14:51,766
Nevadi ti to pro studiu?

229
00:14:51,766 --> 00:14:52,392
Vis.

230
00:14:53,101 --> 00:14:54,561
Nemam moc penez,vis...

231
00:14:54,894 --> 00:14:57,731
Opravdu? Ale vzdyt bydlis v takove ohromne rezidenci.

232
00:14:58,148 --> 00:14:59,858
Jo ten dum je velky.

233
00:15:00,859 --> 00:15:03,278
Bydlim tam jen ja a dedecek

234
00:15:03,319 --> 00:15:06,698
Na druhou stranu,chci si taky videlat svoje vlastni penize.

235
00:15:08,366 --> 00:15:10,160
Pristi zastavka je...

236
00:15:12,495 --> 00:15:14,205
Dedo, jsem doma.

237
00:15:14,914 --> 00:15:18,376
Vitej doma, Hiroyuki.

238
00:15:21,463 --> 00:15:23,131
Tehdy to bylo vydet

239
00:15:23,131 --> 00:15:26,676
ze deda byl kazdym dnem starsi.

240
00:15:27,052 --> 00:15:29,888
zivot se starsim clovekem

241
00:15:29,888 --> 00:15:34,267
V mire jak se deda staval starsi,tak ja jsem byl stale
vetsi

242
00:15:34,684 --> 00:15:37,145
Bylo to dost zvlastni tehdy....

243
00:15:37,145 --> 00:15:40,732
ze se chci stat uz dospely.

244
00:15:40,774 --> 00:15:44,944
Nechci byt je dedou,ktery se o nekoho stara

245
00:15:44,944 --> 00:15:49,657
Chtel jsem byt uz dospely a silny,

246
00:15:50,658 --> 00:15:55,246
Chtel jsem aby uz ho nic nebolelo.
Chtel jsem mu poridit odborneho lekare..

247
00:15:55,288 --> 00:15:59,417
Chtel jsem aby mohl poradne jist,a aby
si mohl odpocinout..

248
00:15:59,542 --> 00:16:03,421
Chtel jsem se mu odvdecit za tu lasku se kterou
se o me staral cely ten cas

249
00:16:03,463 --> 00:16:07,050
Kdy bych byl dospely,mel
bych vetsi sanci to udelat.

250
00:16:10,637 --> 00:16:13,264
Mozna by se na tebe mel podivat doktor

251
00:16:14,182 --> 00:16:17,477
Neboj se o me,
neni to nic vazneho,
nema cenu delat rozruch.

252
00:16:18,812 --> 00:16:20,772
Bud klidny,
stejne uz musis jit do skoly.

253
00:16:21,815 --> 00:16:22,524
Dobre.

254
00:16:26,653 --> 00:16:29,906
Tak hodne jsi vyrostl.

255
00:16:30,949 --> 00:16:35,412
Vzdyt jeste pred chvili jsi byl maly chlapec.

256
00:16:36,121 --> 00:16:38,540
Ted uz s tebou musim mluit jako s dospelym.

257
00:16:39,332 --> 00:16:43,211
Jake je zvlastni ze o tom premyslim teprve ted.

258
00:16:52,554 --> 00:16:54,014
Oh, Hiro.

259
00:17:25,503 --> 00:17:26,504
Dedo?

260
00:17:53,198 --> 00:17:57,786
Hiro, vsichni lide co prisli na pohreb,uz sli.

261
00:17:58,912 --> 00:18:00,705
Musis byt hodne unaveny a hladovy.

262
00:18:01,331 --> 00:18:02,374
Co bys chtel snist?

263
00:18:02,957 --> 00:18:05,710
Vsechno je v poradku.
Dekuji ti za vsechno.

264
00:18:06,127 --> 00:18:09,130
Poradim si sam.
Prosim jdi uz domu.

265
00:18:10,256 --> 00:18:14,636
Ale Hiro,nemuzes nic nejist,
Onemocnis.

266
00:18:15,303 --> 00:18:18,098
Dekuji,ale to nevadi.
Vsechno bude dobre

267
00:18:19,599 --> 00:18:20,725
Jdi uz domu.

268
00:19:05,520 --> 00:19:07,022
Proc tu porad si?

269
00:19:10,358 --> 00:19:11,359
Proc tady sakra porad..

270
00:19:11,359 --> 00:19:12,318
Protoze..

271
00:19:14,654 --> 00:19:16,281
... chci byt s tebou.

272
00:19:24,539 --> 00:19:25,623
Blazne...

273
00:19:28,918 --> 00:19:30,879
Proc jsem pro nho nikdy nemel cas!

274
00:19:31,671 --> 00:19:33,465
Tak moc ho mam rad,

275
00:19:34,924 --> 00:19:36,968
ale nic jsem pro nho neudelal!

276
00:19:37,927 --> 00:19:39,095
Vzdy jsem se bal,

277
00:19:40,430 --> 00:19:43,767
ze me jednoho dne dedecek opusti,

278
00:19:45,352 --> 00:19:47,937
a chtel jsem jeste pro nho tolik udelat.

279
00:19:48,563 --> 00:19:49,981
A ted...

280
00:19:52,025 --> 00:19:55,403
To boli,
protoze mu nemuzu nic dat

281
00:19:56,696 --> 00:20:00,033
Tolik planu...

282
00:20:00,283 --> 00:20:02,077
a nic z toho nevyslo!

283
00:20:10,168 --> 00:20:14,673
Jesli si to takhe myslis ,tak ale 
tvuj dedecek si to mohl myslet jinak.

284
00:20:16,883 --> 00:20:19,886
Jsem si jista ze te miloval,vic nez cokoliv na svete.

285
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:22,639
Radost mu delalo samo to ze,

286
00:20:22,639 --> 00:20:25,725
nejsi sam na tomhle svete..

287
00:20:26,059 --> 00:20:28,478
Tak hluboka byla laska tveho dedy.

288
00:20:29,396 --> 00:20:35,735
Nebo myslis ze bych mohla nahradit misto
tveho dedy?
Byt vzdy po tvem boku?

289
00:20:38,071 --> 00:20:42,409
Tak tedy, cekali jsme az Miyako
skonci skolu,

290
00:20:42,409 --> 00:20:44,411
a pripravili se na svatbu-

291
00:20:47,747 --> 00:20:51,167
Rok nato se nam narodila dcerka,a
potom rok od roku dalsi.

292
00:20:51,668 --> 00:20:54,462
Nemeli jsme moc penez,
ale byli jsme stastni..

293
00:20:56,715 --> 00:20:59,134
Ted rozumim tomu co rikal deda

294
00:20:59,801 --> 00:21:01,803
Kdyz deda ma deti

295
00:21:02,095 --> 00:21:03,930
Jsem stastny,ze to tak je.

296
00:21:05,181 --> 00:21:10,437
Duch dedy,jde pres me do mojich dcer

297
00:21:11,938 --> 00:21:14,065
Protoze laska je cit,ktery se porad rozrusta.

298
00:21:16,735 --> 00:21:19,446
Tvuj dum je nyni knihovna

299
00:21:20,447 --> 00:21:21,990
No nic,nemohu za to

300
00:21:21,990 --> 00:21:24,492
Nemohl jsem ten dum zadrzet pro sebe.

301
00:21:24,951 --> 00:21:27,078
Dobrou chut!

302
00:21:33,168 --> 00:21:37,172
Tato, nejsi uz takovy mlady,prosim nepospichej,a
jez s nami.

303
00:21:37,505 --> 00:21:38,965
To je pravda!

304
00:21:38,965 --> 00:21:39,716
Ne proc.

305
00:21:40,300 --> 00:21:43,053
To je konec,kdyz se o tebe zacinaji deti bat.

306
00:21:43,595 --> 00:21:45,263
Chce vsechno delat po svem

307
00:21:45,638 --> 00:21:49,517
Dej pokoj, nebo je cas kdy si des vymenit plenky?
Muze je menit najednou!

308
00:21:50,894 --> 00:21:53,104
Drz zobak, frajere!

309
00:21:54,147 --> 00:21:55,273
Otce!

310
00:21:55,940 --> 00:21:57,984
Opravdu! Jak dlouho minis byt jeste nastvany kvuli te zprave?.

311
00:21:57,984 --> 00:22:01,279
Och, bud tise!
Me nepremluvis!

312
00:22:01,279 --> 00:22:02,781
Otce, tady mas trochu ryze.

313
00:22:03,823 --> 00:22:06,076
Uklidni se. To nema cenu

314
00:22:06,951 --> 00:22:09,788
Laska je neco,co se porad rozrusta.

315
00:24:14,913 --> 00:24:27,533
Titulky klobaska

